An Act relative to hunting near a dwelling.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General Court assembled, and by the authority
of the same, as follows:
1 Section 58 of chapter 131 of the General Laws, as appearing in the 2016 Official Edition,
2 is hereby amended by inserting, in line 6, after the word "thereof" the following words:-
